---
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <p class="hero-tag">Web AI Advisory</p>
      <h1 class="hero-headline">Web・AIのことは、<br />プロに聞こう。</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">サイト改善、AI導入、マーケティング。<br class="hide-mobile" />月額2万円〜で、御社専属のWeb・AI参謀がつきます。</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="https://cal.37d.jp/37design/ai%E7%9B%B8%E8%AB%87" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-primary">
          <span>無料面談を予約する</span>
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none"><path d="M2 7H12M8 3L12 7L8 11" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/lp/ai-assessment/" class="btn-outline">AI活用度を診断</a>
      </div>
      <p class="hero-note">初回無料 / オンライン完結 / 契約期間の縛りなし</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="stat">
        <p class="stat-num">50+</p>
        <p class="stat-label">Clients</p>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <p class="stat-num">98%</p>
        <p class="stat-label">Satisfaction</p>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <p class="stat-num">'12</p>
        <p class="stat-label">Since</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    background: #fff;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
  }
  .hero-inner {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 4rem;
  }
  .hero-text { flex: 1; }

  .hero-tag {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: #cc8800;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .hero-headline {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #111;
    line-height: 1.25;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: clamp(13px, 1.8vw, 15px);
    color: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    line-height: 1.9;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .hero-note {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .hero-stats {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1px;
    background: #e8e8e8;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .stat {
    background: #fff;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1.5rem 2.5rem;
  }
  .stat-num {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #111;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    color: rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 6px;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    background: #111;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 13px 28px;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: #cc8800; }

  .btn-outline {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    color: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 13px 28px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-outline:hover { border-color: #111; color: #111; }

  .hide-mobile { display: none; }

  @media (min-width: 769px) {
    .hide-mobile { display: inline; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero { padding: 3rem 1.5rem; }
    .hero-inner { flex-direction: column; gap: 2.5rem; align-items: flex-start; }
    .hero-stats { flex-direction: row; width: 100%; }
    .stat { flex: 1; padding: 1.25rem 1rem; }
    .stat-num { font-size: 28px; }
  }
</style>
